sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor U as User
  participant G as Gateway
  participant A as Auth
  participant R as Redis OTP
  participant N as Notify gateway

  U->>G: Request OTP phone
  G->>A: Start OTP
  A->>R: Store code TTL
  A->>N: Send SMS
  N-->>U: OTP SMS
  U->>G: Submit code
  G->>A: Verify
  A->>R: Read delete
  A-->>G: JWT refresh
  G-->>U: Tokens cookie body
